[0-4] Suddenly, the view shifts. The zombie is now on a white platform that extends outward in front of a backdrop of a blue sky and white clouds. A line of Minecraft mobs stand behind glass panels on the platform. From left to right, there is a brown bat, followed by blaze, guardian, and wither. Each mob is contained in a different colored glass panel. The zombie begins walking toward the blaze mob.
